          </list-item>
          <list-item>
            <p>Total parenteral nutrition</p>
          </list-item>
          <list-item>
            <p>Drugs &#x00026; Toxins - oral contraceptives, rifampin, probenecid, steroids, chlorpromazine, herbal medications (e.g., Jamaican bush tea, kava kava), arsenic</p>
          </list-item>
          <list-item>
